Package org.tiralab.particles

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GuiListener
    This interface allows the App class to hook up code into the gui events.
    Model
    The classes, which implement Model interface, store the actual particles.
    Storage
    The acceleration structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    This class handles the program logic for the gui.
    ArrayStorage
    Array based particle storage.
    DirectStorage
    This is dummy acceleration structure that just gets the particles from the model and puts them into a array.
    Fluid
    This class is model for simple fluid simulation.
    Particle
    Store information about single particle.
    ParticleArray
    The dynamic array.
    ParticleSet
    This class is set for particle objects.
    Rectangle
    A immutable rectangle class.
    Stars
    Nbody simulator.
    Testing
    The commandline interface for the program.
    TreeStorage
    This acceleration structure stores the particles in quadtree.
    Window
    Window class renders the whole gui.
